{"words":[{"word":"joke","count":4},{"word":"oh","count":3},{"word":"rest","count":2},{"word":"coin","count":2},{"word":"saying","count":2},{"word":"perhaps","count":2},{"word":"captain","count":2},{"word":"known","count":2},{"word":"give","count":2},{"word":"male","count":2},{"word":"boy","count":2},{"word":"female","count":2},{"word":"girl","count":2},{"word":"playing","count":2},{"word":"lost","count":2},{"word":"days","count":2},{"word":"andreas","count":2},{"word":"thing","count":2},{"word":"old","count":2},{"word":"shame","count":2},{"word":"ah","count":1},{"word":"toscanini","count":1},{"word":"night","count":1},{"word":"watcher","count":1},{"word":"hahaha","count":1},{"word":"remembers","count":1},{"word":"ever","count":1},{"word":"mad","count":1},{"word":"sailor","count":1},{"word":"raved","count":1},{"word":"captain's","count":1},{"word":"lead","count":1},{"word":"untold","count":1},{"word":"treasures","count":1},{"word":"holding","count":1},{"word":"exist","count":1},{"word":"alright","count":1},{"word":"golden","count":1},{"word":"conquered","count":1},{"word":"every","count":1},{"word":"sea","count":1},{"word":"man","count":1},{"word":"wealth","count":1},{"word":"amassed","count":1},{"word":"lives","count":1},{"word":"leisure","count":1},{"word":"luxury","count":1},{"word":"raise","count":1},{"word":"fine","count":1},{"word":"point","count":1},{"word":"half","count":1},{"word":"haha","count":1},{"word":"perfect","count":1},{"word":"timing","count":1},{"word":"dear","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"new","count":1},{"word":"play","count":1},{"word":"works","count":1},{"word":"dire","count":1},{"word":"nimble","count":1},{"word":"hero","count":1},{"word":"splendid","count":1},{"word":"young","count":1},{"word":"acolyte","count":1},{"word":"anxious","count":1},{"word":"grappling","count":1},{"word":"faith","count":1},{"word":"future","count":1},{"word":"nonsense","count":1},{"word":"love","count":1},{"word":"watching","count":1},{"word":"walk","count":1},{"word":"wire","count":1},{"word":"everyone's","count":1},{"word":"cup","count":1},{"word":"tea","count":1},{"word":"partners","count":1},{"word":"long","count":1},{"word":"chemistry","count":1},{"word":"punchline","count":1},{"word":"landed","count":1},{"word":"yet","count":1},{"word":"laughed","count":1},{"word":"said","count":1},{"word":"become","count":1},{"word":"twenty-first","count":1},{"word":"twenty","count":1},{"word":"ha","count":1},{"word":"good","count":1},{"word":"otherwise","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"ruffled","count":1},{"word":"order's","count":1},{"word":"feathers","count":1},{"word":"ended","count":1},{"word":"pilgrim's","count":1},{"word":"sail","count":1},{"word":"branded","count":1},{"word":"fool","count":1},{"word":"dull","count":1},{"word":"credit-counting","count":1},{"word":"merchant","count":1},{"word":"life","count":1},{"word":"admit","count":1},{"word":"bit","count":1},{"word":"dark","count":1},{"word":"nineteen","count":1},{"word":"technical","count":1},{"word":"terms","count":1},{"word":"survivor's","count":1},{"word":"guilt-induced","count":1},{"word":"awkwardness","count":1},{"word":"syndrome","count":1},{"word":"many","count":1},{"word":"newcomers","count":1},{"word":"troupe","count":1},{"word":"fools","count":1},{"word":"treatment","count":1},{"word":"brant","count":1},{"word":"i'd","count":1},{"word":"nimbus","count":1},{"word":"chorales","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"song's","count":1},{"word":"forever","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Ah, Toscanini, the Night Watcher. Hahaha. You're one of the few who still remembers him.","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Did he ever tell you the rest? That mad sailor who raved about his captain's coin, saying it would lead to untold treasures.","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Perhaps it's the very coin our Captain here is holding.","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Oh, they exist, alright. The Golden Captain conquered every sea known to man. The wealth he amassed could give us all lives of leisure and luxury.","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"You raise a fine point. Where is the other half…","quest_name":"Sail Day, Captain!","quest_id":155000000},{"text":"Haha, perfect timing, dear {Male=boy;Female=girl}! I've got a new play in the works, and I'm in dire need of a nimble hero!","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"And you, you'd be splendid too! How about playing a young Acolyte, lost and anxious, grappling with her faith and future?","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"Nonsense, are you saying you don't love watching them now? Well, these days I do walk the wire. Perhaps not everyone's cup of tea.","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"Andreas! We've been partners for how long now? Where's the chemistry? My punchline hasn't landed yet!","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"No, no, the {Male=boy;Female=girl} laughed at what I just said. I myself have become the twenty-first joke, so only twenty more to go now!","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"Or a joke?","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"Ha, good thing you didn't! Otherwise, he'd never have ruffled the Order's feathers and ended up on a Pilgrim's Sail branded as a Fool. He'd just be a dull, Credit-counting merchant the rest of his life.","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"Well, I admit that one was a bit dark, but a joke is a joke. That's nineteen.","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"In technical terms, this is known as the Survivor's Guilt-induced Awkwardness Syndrome. Many newcomers to the Troupe of Fools have it. Give her the old treatment, Andreas.","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"Oh Brant, how could you do such a thing? For shame!","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002},{"text":"Oh, back in the old days, I'd be playing the Nimbus Chorales at a time like this. Such a shame the song's now lost forever!","quest_name":"Morning Star III","quest_id":189800002}]}